<template>
  <v-autocomplete @input="emitInput" :items="items" item-text="name" item-value="id" />
</template>

<script>
export default {
  data() {
    return {
      items: [
        { id: 1, name: 'Alice' },
        { id: 2, name: 'Bob' },
        { id: 3, name: 'Charlie' },
      ],
    };
  },
  methods: {
    emitInput(value) {
      this.$emit('input', value.id);
    },
  },
};
</script>
